               <p>THOMAS HEAPLEY. I live in <placeName id="t18260406-270-crimeloc1458">St. John's-wood-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-270-crimeloc1458" type="placeName" value="St. John's-wood-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-270-crimeloc1458" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-270-off1456 t18260406-270-crimeloc1458"></join>. About nine o'clock in the morning of the 3d of March, I was in the first floor of my house - the child came to say two boys had got over the wall - I ran down stairs with my son and desired him to get over the wall and see what they were about - he got over and called me - I jumped over and saw the prisoner and another, who had got these things, which had been taken from the back of my garden, into the field - I had seen them safe forty-eight hours before, but they were not on the spot where I found them twenty-four hours before - the prisoner fell on his knees, and hoped I would forgive him - he said it was the first time he ever was found taking any thing.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260406-270-person1470">
                  JOHN 
                  HEAPLEY
               <interp inst="t18260406-270-person1470" type="surname" value="HEAPLEY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260406-270-person1470" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260406-270-person1470" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner and another boy breaking up a cast-iron gutter - I gave the alarm, and went down and found the property over the wall - the prisoner and the other were carrying it - I heard him beg forgiveness.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260406-270-person1471">
                  ROBERT 
                  WILLIAMS
               <interp inst="t18260406-270-person1471" type="surname" value="WILLIAMS"></interp>
